An attempted assault on an investigative police officer ended with a shootout that ended with three people injured in the commune of Santiago. According to information from the PDI, the incident occurred last night at the intersection of Santa Isabel and Carmen streets, when the individuals approached the victim to perpetrate a portonazo. \At that moment, the officer took out his service weapon and shot the three criminals on his legs. He perpetrated his weapon about five times to avoid the theft of his car.
The three individuals shot were taken to a health center. The fact generated great expectation among passers-by. 